Quarter-Life is an FPS game which is a parody to Valve's Half-Life.
(Don't take it wrong, we love Half-Life.)

Libraries used
==============
Ogre3D (http://ogre3d.org/) - rendering engine
Bullet Physics (http://bulletphysics.org/) - physics simulation and collision engine
FMOD (http://fmod.org/) - audio library
CEGUI (http://cegui.org.uk) - GUI library
Boost (http://boost.org) - various libraries

Made primarily for Linux.


Find more info at homepage of Quarter-Life at http://codefreax.org/projects/Quarter-Life.
